The paper proposes a convolutional neural network (CNN)-based method for patent image retrieval, which involves visual material type prediction and International Patent Classification (IPC) class label prediction. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. Finally, the paper also involves engineering design, which suggests that it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
